## Build Instructions:

After navigating into the assign1 directory, compile the program using the following command:

    $ g++ src/*.cpp src/entity/*.cpp -o server -std=c++11 -lwthttp -lwt -lboost_system

## Run Instructions:

    $ ./server --docroot ./html --http-address localhost --http-port 8080

Make sure to specify ./html as the docroot as it contains custom CSS files.
